txt.en: My snowflakes! You have skilfully dislodged [placeholder] of them in the last minute of our jolly contest!
You dids't mantain a tempestuous rate of [placeholder] snowflakes for each moment over the span of our game.
Thou hast dislodged roughly [placeholder] snowflakes with each passing second!
I have lost [placeholder] snowflakes to your blows! A joyous resolution to our yuletide tournament!
\qI yield - Thy spirit is unmatched! Now give me a few moments to recollect some snow, lest I melt away entirely.\q
Merry Yule! Shall we exchange a boisterous flurry of blows to celebrate the season?
